snippet.title: THE SCARIEST DDLC MOD EVER! | Doki Doki Nightmare (DDLC Mods)
snippet.description:
Doki Doki Nightmare! This could be one of the scariest DDLC Mods ever. I think DDLC Mods should start doing more horror in general. This is a ddlc horror mod... Therefore it is unique. It was quite scary too. There are rarely DDLC mods that feature horror, so this is definitely an awesome thing! DDLC Horror makes a comeback in this mod.

Doki Doki Nightmare (DDLC Mod) Download: https://www.reddit.com/r/DDLCMods/comments/axrhqu/a_new_mod_ready_to_play_ddlc_nightmare/

My Discord: https://discord.gg/fkYvhte
My Twitter: https://twitter.com/KuudereGhost
My Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kuudereghost

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Song: NIVIRO - The Ghost [NCS Release] 
Music provided by NoCopyrightSounds.
Video: https://youtu.be/lTEzfj8IAR0
